          <unittitle>Advisory Committee</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Advisory Committee is the body which oversees the running of the airport for the Ann Arbor City Council. The series spans the years 1972 to 1995. It contains the minutes of committee meetings, resolutions and material relating to issues discussed at the meetings. The expansion of the airport was the largest issue the committee had to deal with so there is some material which complements the Expansion series.</p>
